  <entry>
    <title>高数复习第一章第五节</title>
    <link href="/post/%E9%AB%98%E6%95%B0%E5%A4%8D%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E7%AB%A0%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%94%E8%8A%82.html"/>
    <url>/post/%E9%AB%98%E6%95%B0%E5%A4%8D%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E7%AB%A0%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%94%E8%8A%82.html</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="极限运算法则"><a href="#极限运算法则" class="headerlink" title="极限运算法则"></a>极限运算法则</h1><h2 id="Th1："><a href="#Th1：" class="headerlink" title="Th1："></a>Th1：</h2><p>有限个无穷小的和仍未无穷小</p><h2 id="Th2："><a href="#Th2：" class="headerlink" title="Th2："></a>Th2：</h2><p>有界函数与无穷小的乘积仍为无穷小</p><p>例：<script type="math/tex">\lim_{x\to\infty}{\frac{sinx}{x}}=0, \lim_{x\to\infty}{\frac{arctanx}{x}}=0</script></p><h3 id="推论一："><a href="#推论一：" class="headerlink" title="推论一："></a>推论一：</h3><p>常数与无穷小的乘积为无穷小</p><h3 id="推论二："><a href="#推论二：" class="headerlink" title="推论二："></a>推论二：</h3><p>有限个无穷小的乘积为无穷小(把一个当成无穷小，其余当成有界)</p><h2 id="Th3"><a href="#Th3" class="headerlink" title="Th3:"></a>Th3:</h2><p>如果<script type="math/tex">\lim_{}f(x)=A, \lim_{}g(x)=B</script>，且为同一极限过程则：</p><p>1)<script type="math/tex">\lim_{}[f(x)±g(x)]=\lim_{}f(x)±\lim_{}g(x)</script></p><p class="note note-danger">注：要拆开时必须保证每一个极限都存在，即f(x)与g(x)的极限都存在</p><p>2)<script type="math/tex">\lim_{}[f(x)g(x)]=\lim_{}f(x) · \lim_{}g(x)</script></p><p>3)如果<script type="math/tex">\lim_{}{\frac{f(x)}{g(x)}}=\frac{\lim_{}f(x)}{\lim_{}g(x)}</script></p><h3 id="推论一：-lim-cf-x-c-lim-f-x-，c为常数"><a href="#推论一：-lim-cf-x-c-lim-f-x-，c为常数" class="headerlink" title="推论一：\lim_{}[cf(x)]=c\lim_{}f(x)，c为常数"></a>推论一：<script type="math/tex">\lim_{}[cf(x)]=c\lim_{}f(x)，c为常数</script></h3><h3 id="推论二：-lim-f-x-n-lim-f-x-n"><a href="#推论二：-lim-f-x-n-lim-f-x-n" class="headerlink" title="推论二：\lim_{}[f(x)]^n=[\lim_{}f(x)]^n"></a>推论二：<script type="math/tex">\lim_{}[f(x)]^n=[\lim_{}f(x)]^n</script></h3><h2 id="Th4：-极限的保序性"><a href="#Th4：-极限的保序性" class="headerlink" title="Th4：(极限的保序性)"></a>Th4：(极限的保序性)</h2><p>如果<script type="math/tex">\lim_{}f(x)=a, \lim_{}g(x)=b,则a≥b</script></p><p><img src="https://kenyonyanblog.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/PicBed/极限的保序性.png" srcset="/img/loading.gif" alt="https://kenyonyanblog.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/PicBed/极限的保序性.png"></p><h2 id="Th5：-复合函数的极限运算法则"><a href="#Th5：-复合函数的极限运算法则" class="headerlink" title="Th5：(复合函数的极限运算法则)"></a>Th5：(复合函数的极限运算法则)</h2><p>设y=f[g(x)]在点<script type="math/tex">x_0</script>的某去心领域内有定义，若<script type="math/tex">\lim_{x->x_0}g(x)=u_0, \lim_{u->u_0}f(x)=A, \lim_{x->x_0}f[g(x)]=\lim_{u->u_0}f(x)=A</script></p>]]></content>
    
    
